'''2016年达拉斯市區警察遭枪击案'''，是指在[[美國|美國]][[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[达拉斯|达拉斯]]一场抗議美國警察濫殺黑人的和平示威活动结束后，一名黑人米卡·澤維爾·約翰遜（Micah Xavier Johnson；1991年出生－2016年7月8日）埋伏狙擊維護活動秩序的警察，並試圖枪击12名警察和两名平民以致五名警察遇害的事件。

约翰逊是{{le|美国陆军预备旅|United States Army Reserve|陆军预备旅}}中曾經參與[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|阿富汗战争]]的老兵，据报对最近警方枪杀黑人感到愤怒。警察遇害期间当地正在举行回应连日来分别在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[巴吞鲁日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞鲁日]]和[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]][[法尔考高地_(明尼苏达州)|法尔考高地]]发生的{{le|奥尔顿·斯特灵枪击案|Shooting of Alton Sterling|奥尔顿·斯特灵}}和{{le|费兰多·卡斯蒂利亚枪击案|Shooting of Philando Castile}}的示威活动。

案发后，警方在一处停车场碰到约翰逊，双方随之陷入对峙局面。7月8日凌晨，警方利用装有炸弹的拆弹机器人擺平了约翰逊。有专家认为这是美国史上警方首次利用机器人提供致命武力。这是自[[九一一恐怖袭击|九一一恐怖袭击]]以来[[美国警察|美国警察]]损伤最惨重的遇袭案。

== 背景 ==
这场抗议活动是“[[黑人的命也是命|黑人的命也是命]]”运动的一部分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/dallas-police-sniper-black-lives-matter-478675 |title=Dallas Shootings: Sniper Fire Kills Five Police Officers at Black Lives Matter Protest |publisher=Newsweek |agency=Reuters |date=2016-07-07 |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2016-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709140046/http://www.newsweek.com/dallas-police-sniper-black-lives-matter-478675 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Legum |first=Judd |url=http://thinkprogress.org/justice/2016/07/07/3796562/active-shooter-downtown-dallas-black-lives-matter-protest/ |title=12 Officers Shot, 5 Killed, At Black Lives Matter Protest in Dallas |work=Think Progress |date=2016-07-07 |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709150657/http://thinkprogress.org/justice/2016/07/07/3796562/active-shooter-downtown-dallas-black-lives-matter-protest/ |archive-date=2016-07-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/dont-blame-black-lives-matter-for-the-deaths-of-dallas-cops_us_577f9409e4b01edea78d6514 |script-title=en:Don’t Blame Black Lives Matter For The Deaths Of Dallas Cops |work=The Huffington Post |date=2016-07-08 |accessdate=2016-07-09 |first=Lilly |last=Workneh |archive-date=2016-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708162835/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/dont-blame-black-lives-matter-for-the-deaths-of-dallas-cops_us_577f9409e4b01edea78d6514 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Blair |last=Shiff |url=http://www.wfaa.com/news/dallas-pd-black-lives-matter-protesters-posed-for-photos-before-deadly-ambush/267722139 |title=Dallas PD, Black Lives Matter protesters posed for photos before deadly ambush |work=WFAA |date=2016-07-08 |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2016-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709133754/http://www.wfaa.com/news/dallas-pd-black-lives-matter-protesters-posed-for-photos-before-deadly-ambush/267722139 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，抗议活动由下一代行动网络（{{lang|en|Next Generation Action Network}}）组织。活动前数日，非裔美国人{{le|奥尔顿·斯特灵枪击案|Shooting of Alton Sterling|奥尔顿·斯特灵}}在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]遭警察枪杀，{{le|费兰多·卡斯蒂利亚枪击案|Shooting of Philando Castile|费兰多·卡斯蒂利亚}}在[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]]也同样被警察击毙，此次抗议活动是针对这两次枪击案而发动。<ref name=NYTimes.Identified>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/08/us/dallas-police-officers-killed.html|title=Dallas Police Shooting Suspect Identified; 5 Officers Are Dead|last1=McGee|first1=Patrick|last2=Fernandez|first2=Manny|last3=Bromwich|first3=Jonah Engel|last4=Pérez-Peña|first4=Richard|date=2016-07-07|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|accessdate=2016-07-07|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708084443/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/08/us/dallas-police-officers-killed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一场抗议活动于7月7日全美开展<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/protesters-nationwide-hit-the-streets-against-police-shootings/|title=Eleven officers shot at Dallas protest against police shootings|work=CBS News|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|first=Shanika|last=Gunaratna|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708041542/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/protesters-nationwide-hit-the-streets-against-police-shootings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。达拉斯的抗议活动大约有800人参与，约100名警察被派往活动现场和周边地区<ref name=NBC.Shot/>。案发前，据报无其他事件发生，活动现场平稳有序<ref name=Dallas.Fired>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/shots-fired-at-downtown-rally-to-protest-police-shootings-shooter-armed-and-still-free-cops-say-8469803|title=11 Dallas Police and DART Officers Wounded, 5 Fatally, at Rally to Protest Police Shootings|work=Dallas Observer|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912105028/https://www.dallasobserver.com/news/11-dallas-police-and-dart-officers-wounded-5-fatally-at-rally-to-protest-police-shootings-8469803|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
晚上8点58分，达拉斯市中心开始传出枪声<ref name=StarTelegram.Arrested>{{cite web|url=http://www.star-telegram.com/news/local/community/dallas/article88375577.html|title=5 officers killed, others wounded in Dallas shooting; suspects arrested|work=Star-Telegram|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Lee|last1=Williams|first2=Mitch|last2=Mitchell|first3=Ryan|last3=Osborne|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708092511/http://www.star-telegram.com/news/local/community/dallas/article88375577.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名目击者据报听到50到75声枪响<ref name=Dallas.Fired/>。达拉斯警察局长{{le|大卫·O·布朗|David Brown (police officer)}}表示有些警员腹背中枪，枪手必须对示威路线有一定认知<ref name=StarTelegram.Arrested/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/07/07/two-police-officers-reported-shot-in-downtown-dallas-near-scene-of-earlier-protests/|title='A heartbreaking morning': Snipers shoot 11 police officers in Dallas during protest rally, killing five|work=The Washington Post|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|first=Travis M.|last=Andrews}}</ref>。市长{{le|迈克·罗林斯|Mike Rawlings}}表示枪手从附近大楼的不同楼层开火<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsweek.com/dallas-shooting-micah-johnson-white-people-black-lives-matter-police-sniper-479082|title=Dallas Police Shooting: Inside the Mind of Micah Johnson|publisher=Newsweek|agency=Reuters|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709074113/http://www.newsweek.com/dallas-shooting-micah-johnson-white-people-black-lives-matter-police-sniper-479082|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少12名警察前往支援<ref name=DallasObserver.Release>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/dallas-police-release-additional-details-about-cop-shooter-micah-johnson-8472095|title=Dallas Police Release Additional Details About Cop Shooter Micah Johnson|work=Dallas Observer|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-09|first=Stephen|last=Young|archive-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710144319/http://www.dallasobserver.com/news/dallas-police-release-additional-details-about-cop-shooter-micah-johnson-8472095|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一名从他的酒店阳台录下事件手机影片的目击者据报观察到枪手穿着战术服装，配有步枪，位于大街上。他表示枪手为他的步枪装好子弹，开始胡乱地开枪，以吸引他附近的警察。当一名警察走近街角时，枪手随即与他交火，迫使警员躲在一根混凝土支柱后面寻找庇护。枪手朝石柱一侧开火，然後跑到另一侧伏击警察，从他身后多次近距离朝他开枪，杀死了他。朝警察尸体补了几枪后，枪手遭遇其他警员的射击，随即逃窜<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/dallas-shooting-witness-ismael-dejesus/|title=Dallas shooting eyewitness: "It looked like an execution"|publisher=CNN|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Tiffany|last=Ap|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708095704/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/dallas-shooting-witness-ismael-dejesus/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BBC.Gunman>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-36751387|title=Dallas shooting: Who was gunman Micah Xavier Johnson?|work=BBC News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2018-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918005551/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-36751387|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

枪战过后，枪手被子弹击中，逃入附近一处停车场。满身是血的他被警方碰到，警方随即朝他开枪，明显再次击伤他<ref name=NBCDFW.Laughed/>。随后枪手与警方在停车场对峙，时不时朝他们开枪。一名警察在枪战中负伤。车库附近发现的一个可疑包裹被拆弹小组保护<ref name=NBC.Shot>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/protests-spawn-cities-across-u-s-over-police-shootings-black-n605686|title=Dallas Police 'Ambush': 12 Officers Shot, 5 Killed During Protest|publisher=NBC News|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|first1=F. Brinley|last1=Bruton|first2=Alexander|last2=Smith|first3=Elizabeth|last3=Chuck|first4=Phil|last4=Helsel|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708041552/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/protests-spawn-cities-across-u-s-over-police-shootings-black-n605686|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CNN.Killed/><ref name=DallasNews.Standoff>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/local-news/20160707-hundreds-expected-at-downtown-dallas-rally-following-shooting-deaths-of-alton-sterling-philando-castile.ece|title=Dallas chief after sniper attack: 'We don't feel much support most days. Let's not make today most days.'|work=The Dallas Morning News|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Claire Z.|last=Cardona|archive-date=2016-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829064902/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/local-news/20160707-hundreds-expected-at-downtown-dallas-rally-following-shooting-deaths-of-alton-sterling-philando-castile.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NBCDFW.Laughed>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcdfw.com/news/local/Dallas-Police-Identify-Gunman-in-Dallas-Protest-Shootings-386015971.html|title=Lone Gunman Laughed, Sang During Standoff: Sources|work=NBC DFW|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|first1=Todd L.|last1=Davis|first2=Scott|last2=Friedman|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709024129/http://www.nbcdfw.com/news/local/Dallas-Police-Identify-Gunman-in-Dallas-Protest-Shootings-386015971.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警察局长布朗后来表示枪手曾宣布尾声将接近，表明他的目的是想杀死更多的警察，还说整个停车场和达拉斯市中心都埋了炸弹<ref name=StarTelegram.Arrested/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/gunman-dead-after-five-police-killed-10495445|title=Gunman 'Blasted Out' After Five Police Killed|publisher=Sky News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708092207/http://news.sky.com/story/gunman-dead-after-five-police-killed-10495445|dead-url=no}}</ref>。执法人员表示枪手“对峙期间边笑边唱歌，一点也不担心”<ref name=NBCDFW.Laughed/>。

谈判期间，约翰逊表示他单独行动，不隶属于任何组织。他据报只想跟黑人警察说话。谈判失败后<ref name=CNN.Reclusive>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/micah-xavier-johnson-dallas-shooter/|title=Dallas police shooter a reclusive Army reservist|work=CNN|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|first1=Nicole|last1=Gaouette|first2=Steve|last2=Visser|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709143938/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/micah-xavier-johnson-dallas-shooter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，对峙于次日凌晨2点30分结束<ref name=LATimes.Journal>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-dallas-police-shooting-20160708-snap-story.html|title='Loner' Dallas gunman had bomb materials and kept journal of combat tactics|work=The Los Angeles Times|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Molly|last1=Hennessy-Fiske|first2=Del Quentin|last2=Wilber|first3=Matt|last3=Pearce|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708142416/http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-dallas-police-shooting-20160708-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，枪手被{{le|炸弹处置|Bomb disposal}}[[遥控车|遥控车]]引爆的约1磅重的[[C4炸药|C4炸药]]杀死<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dpdbeat.com/2016/07/08/investigative-update-regarding-the-deadly-attack-on-police-officers/|title=Investigative Update Regarding the Deadly Attack on Police Officers|accessdate=2016-07-09|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708220957/https://dpdbeat.com/2016/07/08/investigative-update-regarding-the-deadly-attack-on-police-officers/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NBCDFW.Laughed/><ref name=Axe>{{cite web | url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/07/08/cops-kill-with-a-robot-for-the-1st-time.html | title=Cops Kill With a Robot for the 1st Time | work=Daily Beast | date=2016-07-08 | accessdate=2016-07-08 | last=Axe | first=David | archive-date=2016-07-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708174820/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/07/08/cops-kill-with-a-robot-for-the-1st-time.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=robots>* {{cite news|url=http://www.kmtv.com/news/national/there-are-four-suspects-in-the-dallas-police-officer-shootings|title=1 suspect in Dallas shootings dies|date=2016-07-08|publisher=KMTV|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121162847/http://www.kmtv.com/news/national/there-are-four-suspects-in-the-dallas-police-officer-shootings|dead-url=no}}
* {{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/video/dallas-police-used-bomb-robot-to-take-down-gunman-who-shot-cops-721129539651|title=Dallas Police Used Bomb Robot to Take Down Gunman Who Shot Cops|publisher=NBC News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708134606/http://www.nbcnews.com/video/dallas-police-used-bomb-robot-to-take-down-gunman-who-shot-cops-721129539651|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=MacNeal>{{cite web|url=http://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/suspect-killed-bomb-robot|title=Chief: Dallas Shooting Suspect Killed When Police Robot Detonated Bomb|work=Talking Points Memo|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|last=MacNeal|first=Caitlin|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708173755/http://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/suspect-killed-bomb-robot|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Yahoo.Slain>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/three-officer-fatally-shot-during-000000452.html|script-title=en:Dallas sniper shooting: 5 police officers slain, suspect ID’d as Army vet Micah Johnson|work=Yahoo! News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Jason|last=Sickles|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708094848/https://www.yahoo.com/news/three-officer-fatally-shot-during-000000452.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。清查达拉斯市中心时没发现爆炸物。

