'''米卡·泽维尔·约翰逊'''（{{lang|en|Micah Xavier Johnson}}，约1991年－2016年7月8日）与母亲居住于[[梅斯基特_(德克萨斯州)|梅斯基特]]<ref name=NYTimes.Identified/><ref name=BBC.Gunman/><ref name=DallasNews.Standoff/>。他四岁时，父母离婚。{{le|梅斯基特独立学区|Mesquite Independent School District}}表示，约翰逊就读于{{le|约翰·霍恩高中|John Horn High School}}，参与该校[[美国少年后备役军官训练营|美国少年后备役军官训练营]]计划<ref name=DallasNews.Know>{{cite web|url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/crime/headlines/20160708-five-things-you-should-know-about-dallas-shooting-suspect-micah-johnson.ece|title=Five things you should know about Dallas shooting suspect Micah Johnson|work=The Dallas Morning News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Lauren|last1=McGaughy|first2=Brittney|last2=Martin|archive-date=2016-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905090837/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/crime/headlines/20160708-five-things-you-should-know-about-dallas-shooting-suspect-micah-johnson.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，他从高中毕业<ref name=NBC.Loner/>。

2009年3月到2015年4月，约翰逊服役于{{le|美国陆军预备队|U.S. Army Reserve}}，曾任木工和石工专家<ref name="nprwhatweknow">{{cite news | url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/07/08/485239295/what-we-know-about-the-dallas-suspected-gunman | title=What We Know About The Dallas Suspected Gunman | work=NPR | date=2016-07-08 | accessdate=2016-07-08 | last=Kennedy | first=Merrit | archive-date=2019-01-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106105926/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/07/08/485239295/what-we-know-about-the-dallas-suspected-gunman | dead-url=no }}</ref>。约翰逊获得一等兵军衔后，于2013年11月到2014年7月与第420工兵旅<ref name="Hennigan">{{cite web|first=W.J.|last=Hennigan|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-dallas-police-shooting-live-suspected-gunman-was-a-former-army-1467998432-htmlstory.html|title=Dallas gunman was a former Army Reserve soldier|work=The Los Angeles Times|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327134442/https://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-dallas-police-shooting-live-suspected-gunman-was-a-former-army-1467998432-htmlstory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|被派往阿富汗]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/08/micah-xavier-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect|title=Micah Xavier Johnson: Dallas suspect was Afghanistan war veteran, army says|last1=Jamieson|first1=Amber|last2=Ackerman|first2=Spencer|date=2016-07-08|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328150021/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/08/micah-xavier-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WashPost.Veteran>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/07/08/like-a-little-war-snipers-shoot-11-police-officers-during-dallas-protest-march-killing-five/|title=Five police officers killed in Dallas shooting; suspected attacker was Army veteran|work=The Washington Post|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Tim|last1=Madigan|first2=William|last2=Wan|first3=Mark|last3=Berman|archive-date=2019-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527034325/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/07/08/like-a-little-war-snipers-shoot-11-police-officers-during-dallas-protest-march-killing-five/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年5月，在阿富汗期间，他被指控性骚扰一位女兵，女兵要求对他实施[[禁制令|禁制令]]，并表示他需要心理健康辅导。陆军提起开除军籍的诉讼后，在律师的建议下，他放弃了听证的权利，以换取较轻的罪名。他在军队非光荣退役的提议下被送回美国，这被他的律师看作“非常不寻常”的决定。然而，约翰逊2014年9月{{le|军队退役|Military discharge|光荣退役}}<ref name=NYTimes.Interest>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/09/us/suspect-in-dallas-attack-had-interest-in-black-power-groups.html?_r=0|title=Suspect in Dallas Attack Had Interest in Black Power Groups|work=The New York Times|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Jonathan|last1=Mahler|first2=Julie|last2=Turkewitz|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331124025/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/09/us/suspect-in-dallas-attack-had-interest-in-black-power-groups.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Guardian.Home>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/09/dallas-shooting-more-details-emerge-about-micah-xavier-johnson|title=Dallas sniper profile: Micah Johnson was sent home from Afghanistan|publisher=The Guardian|agency=Associated Press|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709161045/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jul/09/dallas-shooting-more-details-emerge-about-micah-xavier-johnson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

约翰逊因他在阿富汗的执勤期而获得{{le|陆军成就勋章|Achievement Medal}}和{{le|北约勋章|NATO Medal}}<ref name=CNN.Reclusive/><ref name="Hennigan"/>。从阿富汗归国后他离开陆军预备队，去世前一直当智障儿童的助手<ref name=NBC.Loner>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/dallas-police-ambush/dallas-shooter-micah-xavier-johnson-was-army-veteran-n606101|title=Dallas Shooter Micah Johnson Was Army Veteran & 'Loner'|work=NBC News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=William|last1=Arkin|first2=Tracy|last2=Connor|first3=Jim|last3=Miklaszewski|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515183700/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/dallas-police-ambush/dallas-shooter-micah-xavier-johnson-was-army-veteran-n606101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在德克萨斯州没有犯罪记录<ref name=NYTimes.Identified/>。

达拉斯警察局长大卫·O·布朗表示，黑人约翰逊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/micah-xavier-johnson-sister-defends-dallas-rampage-article-1.2704540|title=Micah Xavier Johnson's sister defends shooting rampage in Dallas, says cops deserved it|work=The New York Daily News|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Lauren|last1=Klose|first2=Thomas|last2=Tracy|archive-date=2018-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115085607/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/micah-xavier-johnson-sister-defends-dallas-rampage-article-1.2704540|dead-url=no}}</ref>对[[黑人的命也是命|黑人的命也是命]]运动和最近的警察枪击案感到不满。他曾表示，“他要杀白人，尤其是白人警察”<ref name="ShapiroSuspect"/><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bruton|first1=F. Brinley|last2=Smith|first2=Alexander|last3=Chuck|first3=Elizabeth|last4=Helsel|first4=Phil|title=Dallas Police Ambush Suspect 'Wanted to Kill White People': Police Chief|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/dallas-police-ambush/protests-spawn-cities-across-u-s-over-police-shootings-black-n605686|accessdate=2016-07-08|publisher=NBC News|date=2016-07-08|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503170539/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/dallas-police-ambush/protests-spawn-cities-across-u-s-over-police-shootings-black-n605686|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一位跟约翰逊要好的前同事形容他“从来不信任警察”<ref name=DallasNews.Know/>。警方和一位邻居表示约翰逊曾在他家后院进行军事演习<ref name=NYTimes.Discussed>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/10/us/dallas-quiet-after-police-shooting-but-protests-flare-elsewhere.html|title=Micah Johnson Journal Discussed Shooting Tactics, Dallas Official Says|work=The New York Times|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|first1=Manny|last1=Fernandez|first2=Alan|last2=Blinder|first3=Richard|last3=Pérez-Peña|archive-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710034202/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/10/us/dallas-quiet-after-police-shooting-but-protests-flare-elsewhere.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

调查人员发现约翰逊跟国际恐怖分子与国内极端分子之间没有任何关系<ref name=nprwhatweknow />。然而，对他网上活动的调查揭开了他对黑人民族主义团体的“兴趣”<ref name=NYTimes.Interest/>。约翰逊目前已停用的Facebook主页显示，他“赞”过{{le|新黑豹党|New Black Panther Party}}等黑人民族主义团体的主页，还发表过针对白人的宣泄愤怒帖子<ref name=NBC.Loner/><ref name=Reuters.Posts>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-police-johnson-idUKKCN0ZO2BK|title=Dallas shooting suspect's online posts reflect anger, frustration|work=Reuters|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Gina|last1=Cherelus|first2=Erwin|last2=Seba|first3=Joseph|last3=Ax|first4=Daniel|last4=Trotta|first5=Mimi|last5=Dwyer|first6=Jonathan|last6=Landay|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709001610/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-usa-police-johnson-idUKKCN0ZO2BK|dead-url=no}}</ref>。社区活动家{{le|奎内尔·X|Quanell X}}表示约翰逊曾在新黑豹党的[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]分部工作半年<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.click2houston.com/news/report-2-officers-shot-at-dallas-protest | title=Dallas shooter was ex-member of Houston's New Black Panther party | work=Click 2 Houston | date=2016-07-07 | accessdate=2016-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710150337/http://www.click2houston.com/news/report-2-officers-shot-at-dallas-protest | archive-date=2016-07-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。资料照片显示约翰逊曾在[[黑人权力运动|黑人权力运动]]仪式上举起手臂，还附有黑人权力运动标志的图片和[[泛非主义|泛非主义]]运动旗帜<ref name=NYTimes.Interest/><ref name=Reuters.Posts/>

他赞过的另一个黑人民族主义团体是非裔美国人防御同盟（{{lang|en|African American Defense League}}），其领导人Dr. Mauricelm-Lei Millere在2014年{{le|拉奎安·麦克唐纳枪击案|Shooting of Laquan McDonald}}发生后呼吁谋杀全美警察<ref name=NYTimes.Interest/>。为了回应奥尔顿遭警方杀害事件，该组织“在本周早些时候发布消息鼓励暴力对抗警察”<ref name=Guardian.Home/>。

== 受害者 ==
五名警察遇害，七名警察和两名平民在事件中受伤<ref name=theatlantic20160707>{{cite web|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/07/dallas-protest-shooting/490451/|title=The Dallas Shootings: What We Know|work=The Atlantic|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|first=Matt|last=Ford|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329021021/https://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/07/dallas-protest-shooting/490451/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/two-officers-reportedly-shot-at-black-lives-matter-protests-in-dallas-a7126271.html|title=Dallas shooting: Five officers killed and six wounded by snipers at protest|date=2016-07-07|work=The Independent|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Justin|last1=Carissimo|first2=Feliks|last2=Garcia|first3=Samuel|last3=Osborne|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708125418/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/two-officers-reportedly-shot-at-black-lives-matter-protests-in-dallas-a7126271.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多数在示威期间中枪，至少有一名警察在与约翰逊枪战时中枪<ref name=CNN.Killed>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/philando-castile-alton-sterling-protests/|title=Dallas sniper attack: 5 officers killed, suspect identified|publisher=CNN|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-07|first1=Faith|last1=Karimi|first2=Catherine E.|last2=Shoichet|first3=Ralph|last3=Ellis|quote="Five police officers were killed and seven others were injured in the ambush. It was the deadliest single incident for U.S. law enforcement since September 11, 2001. Two civilians also were wounded in the shootings, the Dallas mayor's office said."|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708050649/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/08/us/philando-castile-alton-sterling-protests/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ksl-deadliest">{{cite news | url = https://www.ksl.com/?sid=40564629&nid=157&title=5-dallas-officers-slain-deadliest-day-for-police-since-911 | title = Dallas suspect amassed personal arsenal at suburban home | first = Will | last = Weissert | date = 2016-07-08 | work = KSL.com | publisher = KSL Broadcasting | location = Salt Lake City | accessdate = 2016-07-08 | archive-date = 2016-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712020919/http://www.ksl.com/?sid=40564629&nid=157&title=5-dallas-officers-slain-deadliest-day-for-police-since-911 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。死者包括一名{{le|达拉斯地区捷运公司|Dallas Area Rapid Transit}}警察和四名[[达拉斯警察局|达拉斯警察局]]警察<ref name="kdfwLive">{{cite news |url=http://video.foxnews.com/v/2553565094001/kdfw---local-coverage-police-shot-in-dallas/?#sp=watch-live |title=KDFW – Local coverage of police shot in Dallas |publisher=KDFW |date=2016-07-07 |accessdate=2016-07-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708111341/http://video.foxnews.com/v/2553565094001/kdfw---local-coverage-police-shot-in-dallas/#sp=watch-live |archivedate=2016-07-08 }}</ref>。四名受伤的警察来自警察局，剩下三名来自捷运公司<ref name=LATimes.Journal/><ref name=WashPost.Veteran/>。部分受伤警察被送往{{le|帕克兰纪念医院|Parkland Memorial Hospital}}，两名警察接受了手术<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/shots-fired-dallas-amid-protest-recent-police-killings/story?id=40422456|title=Dallas Ambush Shooting Was 'Well-Planned' and 'Thought Out,' Police Say|publisher=ABC News|date=2016-07-07|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=David|last1=Caplan|first2=Emily|last2=Shapiro|first3=Morgan|last3=Winsor|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708035745/http://abcnews.go.com/US/shots-fired-dallas-amid-protest-recent-police-killings/story?id=40422456|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遇害警察身份如下：

*警察局高级下士洛恩·阿伦斯（{{lang|en|Lorne Ahrens}}），48岁，2002年入职<ref name=NYTimes.Identified/><ref name=CBS.Officers>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/dallas-officers-dead-newlywed-iraq-veteran/|title=Dallas officers shot to death include newlywed, Iraq veteran|publisher=CBS News|agency=Associated Press|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708191059/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/dallas-officers-dead-newlywed-iraq-veteran/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2016/07/08/slain-dallas-officer-lorne-ahrens-was-a-big-ol-boy-with-a-soft-touch/?utm_term=.49452357a161|title=Slain Dallas Officer Lorne Ahrens was out of surgery when something went wrong|work=The Washington Post|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Steve|last=Hendrix|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822091736/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2016/07/08/slain-dallas-officer-lorne-ahrens-was-a-big-ol-boy-with-a-soft-touch/?utm_term=.49452357a161|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*警察局警官迈克尔·克罗尔（{{lang|en|Michael Krol}}），40岁，前[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[韦恩县_(密歇根州)|韦恩县]][[狱警|狱警]]，2007年入职<ref name=NYTimes.Identified/><ref name=CBS.Officers/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fox2detroit.com/news/dallas-ambush/171701297-story|title=Metro Detroit native Michael Krol among Dallas officers killed|work=FOX 2 Detroit|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007000830/http://www.fox2detroit.com/news/dallas-ambush/171701297-story|archive-date=2016-10-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
