sdate=2016-07-09|first=Suman|last=Varandani|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708100030/http://www.ibtimes.com/dallas-police-shootings-facebook-activates-safety-check-after-black-lives-matter-2390034|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 调查 ===
警方推断约翰逊使用了一把不可拆卸10发弹匣的[[SKS半自动步枪|SKS]][[半自动步枪|半自动步枪]]和一把“大容量手枪”，还穿着[[防弹背心|防弹背心]]<ref name=NYTimes.Discussed/><ref name=Newsday.Rifle>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/news/nation/micah-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect-was-dallas-area-resident-1.12020521|title=Micah Johnson: Dallas sniper used protective vest, semi-automatic rifle in shootings|publisher=Newsday|agency=Associated Press|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708221417/http://www.newsday.com/news/nation/micah-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect-was-dallas-area-resident-1.12020521|dead-url=no}}</ref>。案发翌日，约翰逊家被搜查<ref name="Gregory">{{cite web|url=http://abc7.com/news/dallas-suspect-said-he-wanted-to-kill-white-police-officers-police-say/1418651/|title=Dallas suspect said he was upset over Black Lives Matter, wanted to kill white people|last=Gregory|first=John|date=2016-07-08|publisher=KABC-TV (ABC 7)|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709015436/http://abc7.com/news/dallas-suspect-said-he-wanted-to-kill-white-police-officers-police-say/1418651/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警探在家中发现的制造炸弹的材料、防弹背心、步枪、弹药以及一本含“射击技术和战术动作指南”的“作战战术私人日记”被回收<ref name=LATimes.Journal/><ref name=Yahoo.Slain/><ref name=USAToday.Found>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2016/07/08/multiple-snipers-dallas/86839430/|title=Bomb-making material, ballistic vests, rifles found in Dallas gunman's home|work=USA Today|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Doug|last1=Stanglin|first2=Trevor|last2=Hughes|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708061007/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2016/07/08/multiple-snipers-dallas/86839430/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。200名警察在调查过程中被问话<ref name=DallasObserver.Release/>。

警方最初表示有两名或以上的狙击手参与枪击案，但后来表示约翰逊似乎一直是为孤胆枪手，所有枪声都可以追踪到他。另有三人被警方拘留，“但警方没有说他们可能会起到什么的作用<ref name="ShapiroSuspect"/><ref name="SchmidtLoneGunman">{{cite news|first=Michael S.|last=Schmidt|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/news-dallas-shooting-protest/johnson-was/|title=Attack Appears to Be Work of Lone Gunman, Official Says|work=The New York Times|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709141408/http://www.nytimes.com/live/news-dallas-shooting-protest/johnson-was/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/news/nation/micah-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect-was-dallas-area-resident-1.12020521|title=Micah Johnson: Dallas shooting suspect was Dallas-area resident|work=Newsday|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708221417/http://www.newsday.com/news/nation/micah-johnson-dallas-shooting-suspect-was-dallas-area-resident-1.12020521|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”三人中有两人被看到背着迷彩背包离开拉马尔大街的案发现场。他们跑了六英里后都被截下来拘留<ref name=highspeedchase>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/07/08/us/dallas-police-shooting-map.html|title=How the Attack on the Dallas Police Unfolded|work=The New York Times|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first1=Wilson|last1=Andrews|first2=Larry|last2=Buchanan|first3=K.K. Rebecca|last3=Lai|first4=Jasmine C.|last4=Lee|first5=Adam|last5=Pearce|first6=Julie|last6=Shaver|first7=Derek|last7=Watkins|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708143720/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/07/08/us/dallas-police-shooting-map.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被拘人士后来被确认是或配有武器或携带弹药装备的逃跑示威者<ref name=USAToday.Found/>。然而，警方于7月9日表示他们将继续调查约翰逊是否单独行动，或是与他们密谋枪击案<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/09/us/dallas-ambush-investigation/|title=Dallas police search for suspicious person in headquarters' parking lot|work=CNN|date=2016-07-09|accessdate=2016-07-09|first1=Ralph|last1=Ellis|first2=Steve|last2=Almasy|first3=Steve|last3=Visser|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709164940/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/09/us/dallas-ambush-investigation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 机器人暗杀嫌犯 ===
有专家认为这是美国史上警方首次利用机器人提供致命武力剷除嫌犯<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/jul/08/police-bomb-robot-explosive-killed-suspect-dallas | title=Use of police robot to kill Dallas shooting suspect believed to be first in US history | work=The Guardian | date=2016-07-08 | accessdate=2016-07-08 | last=Thielman | first=Sam | archive-date=2016-07-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708223801/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/jul/08/police-bomb-robot-explosive-killed-suspect-dallas | dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方的Remotec Model F-5<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dpdbeat.com/2016/07/08/investigative-update-regarding-the-deadly-attack-on-police-officers/|title=Investigative Update Regarding the Deadly Attack on Police Officers|date=2016-07-08|work=DPD Beat|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708220957/https://dpdbeat.com/2016/07/08/investigative-update-regarding-the-deadly-attack-on-police-officers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>（炸弹拆除遥控操作载具）绑着一个[[C4炸弹|C4炸弹]]，幹掉了约翰逊并结束对峙<ref name=NBCDFW.Laughed /><ref name=Axe/><ref name=robots/><ref name=MacNeal/><ref name=Yahoo.Slain/>。2016年5月，达拉斯警方据报升级了机器人技术<ref>{{cite web |url=https://dpdbeat.com/2016/05/02/dallas-bomb-squad-gets-upgraded-equipment/ |title=Dallas Bomb Squad Gets Upgraded Equipment |work=The DPD Beat |date=2016-05-02 |accessdate=2016-07-08 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918102313/https://dpdbeat.com/2016/05/02/dallas-bomb-squad-gets-upgraded-equipment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

新美国基金会机器人专家P·W·辛格（{{lang|en|P. W. Singer}}）表示，这是他所知道的首个被警察致命使用的机器人的实例<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sanfrancisco.cbslocal.com/2016/07/08/dallas-police-ambush-robot-kills-suspect-1st/ |title=Using Robot To Kill Dallas Police Shooting Suspect A 1st, Security Expert Says |work=CBS News (San Francisco) |date=2016-07-08 |accessdate=2016-07-08 |archive-date=2016-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709141545/http://sanfrancisco.cbslocal.com/2016/07/08/dallas-police-ambush-robot-kills-suspect-1st/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2016/07/is-it-ok-to-send-a-police-robot-to-deliver-a-bomb-to-kill-an-active-shooter/|title=Dallas deployment of robot bomb to kill suspect is “without precedent”|work=Ars Technica|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Cyrus|last=Farivar|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708224725/http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2016/07/is-it-ok-to-send-a-police-robot-to-deliver-a-bomb-to-kill-an-active-shooter/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popsci.com/police-used-bomb-disposal-robot-to-kill-dallas-shooting-suspect|title=Police Used Bomb Disposal Robot to Kill a Dallas Shooting Suspect|work=Popular Science|date=2016-07-08|accessdate=2016-07-08|first=Dave|last=Gershgorn|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708163449/http://www.popsci.com/police-used-bomb-disposal-robot-to-kill-dallas-shooting-suspect|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[南卡罗来纳大学|南卡罗来纳大学]]法学系助理教授塞斯·斯托顿（{{lang|en|Seth Stoughton}}）表示：“这是警方技术的新开始。机器人已经出现一段时间了，但利用他们递送炸弹引发了一些新问题<ref name=davidagraham>{{cite web |url=http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/07/dallas-police-robot/490478/ |title=The Dallas Shooting and the Advent of Killer Police Robots |work=The Atlantic |first=David A. |last=Graham |date=2016-07-07 |accessdate=2016-07-08 |archive-date=2016-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708200808/http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/07/dallas-police-robot/490478/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

然而，斯托顿表示：“我不知道有警务部门手头上有些打算用作武器的炸弹<ref name=davidagraham/>。”他认为警方利用机器人的方式是合理的，因为约翰逊成为了警方迫在眉睫的威胁，表示：“这种环境证明了每一种基本情形下使用的致命武力<ref name=davidagraham/>。”他补充道，“这也是罪犯或公民使用致命武力敞开大门。我们通常出于多种原因不对美国公民使用炸药，这是非常不负责任的<ref name=CNN.Killed/>。”著名安全研究院马特·布拉泽（{{lang|en|Matt Blaze}}）发布推特表示，他关心如何安全操纵机器人<ref>{{cite tweet|author=Blaze, Matt|number=751416193563693056|user=mattblaze|date=2016-07-08|title=How was the control link to the Dallas bomb robot secured? Stakes go *way* up when something like this is repurposed as a weapon.|accessdate=2016-07-09}}</ref>。

